{{!--
  Radiation chance-of-death result (R1 — Deep Space radiation subsystem). Rendered from
  executeRadiationDeathCheck() and passed as the content of roll.toMessage() (the 1d100 attaches as
  the message roll). `outcomeClause` is the pre-localized win/lose line, carrying a
  result-success / result-fail span (coloured via CSS, not inline style). i18n via CPLocal (mirrors
  drug-save-result.hbs).
--}}
<div class="cyberpunk save-result radiation-death-result">
  <h3>{{CPLocal "RadDeathResultTitle" name=actorName}}</h3>
  <div>{{{CPLocal "RadDeathResultDetail" result=result chance=chance}}}</div>
  <div class="result-line">
    {{{outcomeClause}}}
  </div>
</div>
